---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | David Glass">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Who I Am</h2>
      <p>
        Hello, I'm David Glass. I'm a software developer and cybersecurity professional based in Chicago, focusing on offensive security. With a strong foundation in software development, I have expanded my skills through rigorous training in penetration testing and threat analysis at the Northwestern Cybersecurity Bootcamp.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Cybersecurity Projects</h2>
      <p>
        My cybersecurity work spans cloud architecture, penetration testing, and building security tools. From designing secure Azure deployments to developing an offline "Have I Been Pwned?" service, I apply hands-on skills to real-world security challenges. Explore my <a href="/projects">projects page</a> for details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Beyond Cybersecurity</h2>
      <p>
        Over the years, I've built a variety of projects spanning innovative iOS applications to mathematical research. Here are some highlights:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/coin-problem">Coin Problem</a> &mdash; Mathematical research on the Frobenius Coin Problem, backed by a database of ~60 million sets</li>
        <li><a href="/resume-builder">Resume Builder</a> &mdash; A desktop app for crafting customized, professional resumes</li>
        <li><strong>Ideal Gas Simulator</strong> &mdash; Simulate and visualize particle behavior in an ideal gas</li>
        <li><strong>TradersTool</strong> &mdash; iOS app for calculating trade values between parties (<a href="/privacy/traderstool">privacy policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>AmmoTrac</strong> &mdash; iOS app for tracking ammunition usage and costs at the range (<a href="/privacy/ammotrac">privacy policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Password Tools</strong> &mdash; Random password generator, strength tester, key pair generator, and message encryptor</li>
        <li><strong>Prime Number Checker</strong> &mdash; Web app for checking primality</li>
        <li><strong>Base Conversion Table</strong> &mdash; Versatile base conversion tool</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="label">Email</div>
          <a href="mailto:dglass2525@gmail.com">dglass2525@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="label">GitHub</div>
          <a href="https://github.com/dglass710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/dglass710</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="label">LinkedIn</div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-a-glass/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">linkedin.com/in/david-a-glass</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
